---
import CaseStudy from '../../layouts/CaseStudy.astro';
---

<CaseStudy
  title="Life's Tapestry | CWK. Work"
  description="How CWK. built a digital home for a 64-year-old writer's life's work: launching Life's Tapestry from zero to 47 real subscribers and 25+ published editions in year one."
  category="Lifelong Dream"
  client="Life's Tapestry"
  headline="CWK. Builds a Digital Home for a Writer's Life's Work"
  result="47"
  resultLabel="Real subscribers"
>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="cs-stats">
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">47</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Real Subscribers</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">25+</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Published Editions</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">Year 1</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Foundation built</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>The Story</h2>
    <p>
      A 64-year-old woman with no technical background and no publishing system launched a digital property called Life's Tapestry,
      a place where her stories now live, grow, and reach dozens of readers every week.
    </p>
    <p>
      When she came to CWK., she wasn't trying to build a business. She had simply waited her whole life to write, and this was her moment.
      She had one social account, no brand, no platform, and no way to turn her ideas into something sustainable.
    </p>
    <p>
      CWK. stepped in to build what she didn't have: a home for her intellectual property.
      Instead of chasing followers or pushing monetization, the focus was on building a digital property:
      a place designed to hold her stories, grow an audience, and support future income when she is ready.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Results -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>Results</h2>
    <p>As of January 2026:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>25+ published editions</li>
      <li>47 real subscribers</li>
      <li>Readers who comment, reply, and wait for the next story</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      This isn't content. It's a growing body of work with an audience attached.
      Year one was about building the foundation. The monetization can come later, because the digital property now exists.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>The Bigger Picture</h2>
    <p>
      Life's Tapestry shows what happens when a lifelong dream is given real structure.
      A place for meaningful work to live and compound.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Watch Us Launch Phase 1 -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>Watch Us Launch Phase 1</h2>
    <div class="yt-embed">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GM-G0Cd_fVw?rel=0" title="Life's Tapestry | Phase 1 Launch" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>

</CaseStudy>
